<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
This page is dedicated to simple users who want to discuss macros and inscriptions freely without interfering with the serious work of developpers. <p>
Raw new ideas come here, and developper-approved perfect documents go under <a href="./Documentation">Documentation</a> 
</p>
<p>
Macro and inscriptions exchange categories should have "\Name" links(with the '\') so that they never interfer with official documentation being worked on. 
</p>
